data.description: MINUTES FROM The Woodlands AND LOW TAX RATE!! ROOF 2021! AC 2021! WHOLE HOME GENERATOR! 3 CAR GARAGE! NO BACK NEIGHBORS! BEAUTIFUL THROUGHOUT! DON'T MISS THIS ONE! Discover the unparalleled comfort and charm in this 4-bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home located in the beautiful neighborhood of Stewart's Forest in Conroe. This spacious 3100+ square foot home offers ample space for comfortable living and entertaining; enjoy a movie night in the awesome Media Room or hang out on the large covered back patio while watching the dogs run and play in the big backyard. The game room upstairs is another great space for hanging out! The secluded office downstairs is perfect for working from home or studying. The kitchen is open to the living room and boasts a huge island, gas range and oven and abundant storage space! This fantastic home backs to a lovely greenbelt providing a beautiful wooded view out your back door!
